{"tid":1570344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［遊行要有目標之支線任務］和理勇覺醒","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T10:17:22.000Z","uid":205482,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3c03d5601145df61f5e50a19658754c1907a0873","tid":1570344,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[遊行要有目標] 915 有幾個支線任務大家一齊完成好唔好？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569976</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有一個必做嘅支線任務，就係趁遊行期間，請連登仔女喺現場提醒所有人必須全民勇武 / 覺醒，講到同路人話煩為止！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋當我癡線佬冇問題，但求各位以後盡力減少自身受傷同被捕機會，提高危機意識。人人拎起<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇氣</span></span>出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">必須注意，今日915唔係勇武主場</span><br />\n小弟只係想提醒大家以後平日面對藍絲同休班警時要大大發揮<span style=\"color: gold;\">和你勇精神</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深信呢個方向一定有進步空間，歡迎巴絲打補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">正皮</span>：係連登仔女嘅就做埋呢個支線任務，救救香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">負皮</span>：關我撚事咩，唔係打我就得啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb76cd1c7708a5c45b5b43f6e3c8cec10a631ea","tid":1570344,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"[2百萬人再集結] 915民陣大遊行<br />\n日期：2019年9月15日（日）<br />\n時間：下午 3:00 起步<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n遊行路線：從銅鑼灣東角道起步，遊行至遮打道行人專用區"},{"pid":"2b8b9f1819745433dc9c5872e6878d35403132e1","tid":1570344,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e227fd5c8a85dad73ff9b